## Project Structure

```
antiworm/
├── main.py                  # CLI entry point
├── requirements.txt
├── core/
│   └── engine.py            # Orchestration engine
├── detectors/
│   ├── signature.py         # Signature + hash matching
│   ├── heuristic.py         # Behavioral scoring
│   └── network.py           # Live network monitoring
├── actions/
│   └── quarantine.py        # Quarantine vault manager
├── reports/
│   └── generator.py         # HTML / JSON / TXT reports
├── utils/
│   ├── colors.py            # Terminal colors (cross-platform)
│   ├── banner.py            # CLI banner
│   └── logger.py            # File logging
└── tests/
    └── test_detectors.py    # Unit tests
```

---

## Running Tests

```bash
python -m pytest tests/ -v
```

